{"tid":1889340,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【小鳳姐】48歲男警員確診感染新型冠狀病毒已正式確診！！","createTime":"2020-02-20T15:09:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T15:41:21.000Z","uid":230298,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"15266e396fa86eac28664fa508320a4a91c5fb12","tid":1889340,"uid":230298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T15:09:36.000Z","msg":"衛生防護中心證實一名48歲男警員確診感染新型冠狀病毒，為本港第69宗個案。他居住於油塘油美苑潤美閣，潛伏期內沒有外遊紀錄，其妻子及外母均有病徵。<br />\n<br />\n他於18日開始出現上呼吸道感染病徵，隨即沒有上班，惟同日下午5時30分至晚上10時曾於西環明星海鮮燒鵝專門店出席聚會。<br />\n<br />\n他於19日到訪觀塘社區健康中心求診，經「加強實驗室監測」採集自己的深唾液樣本，今晚確診。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource： TG channel 氣象巴打 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">正式確診囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"d570ecaabbf8b586374c80a773b7c63a51259f75","tid":1889340,"uid":15211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T15:10:03.000Z","msg":"熱烈地彈琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed69ed09f20beecd068a2deac19d4e09e60773fb","tid":1889340,"uid":300006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T15:10:34.000Z","msg":"黑警中招，舉世歡騰"},{"pid":"1fd1e58028cf3eacd3649e5d5eeeffc5a5418b51","tid":1889340,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T15:10:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf29f1db338d91e1d3d9f5618b070f17eb986983","tid":1889340,"uid":104835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T15:11:13.000Z","msg":"希望成枱都係黑警"},{"pid":"30daed9750cddb5ff6fcea92d3d7734f02