15:13:33.000Z","msg":"12點鐘 18區一齊落街開香檳！！"},{"pid":"861461be6fb8c9b5f62fecc9489e688c8699983a","tid":1889340,"uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T15:13:38.000Z","msg":"果隻Popo 有長期病患<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d57813737ebfc4ebf4030bf05ed690374fff9e","tid":1889340,"uid":230298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T15:14:07.000Z","msg":"另外：<br />\n除警員個案外，入住北區醫院的58歲男的士司機亦確診感染新型冠狀病毒，為本港第68宗個案。<br />\n<br />\n他居住於元朗新田石湖圍，潛伏期內沒有外遊紀錄，同住的妻子和兒子沒有病徵。<br />\n<br />\n他於8日起出現上呼吸道感染病徵，10日及17日到訪同一私家診所求醫，18日到訪北區醫院求醫，昨日因在街上昏迷再被送往北區醫院，今日確診。<br />\n<br />\n其的士車牌為JW9897，最後上班日期為16日。曾於上月25日至本月16日乘坐此的士的乘客，建議聯絡衛生防護中心。<br />\n<br />\n#香港新聞 <br />\n#公共衛生情報 #武漢肺炎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsoruce：TG channel 氣象巴打"},{"pid":"e0c5143e7a5b3f68af428a17cc40426885dc68c4","tid":1889340,"uid":145494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T15:14:07.000Z","msg":"一傳十 十傳百<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b6db7d7830538e45302609878fe3f4f71b1c35","tid":1889340,"uid":131459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T15:14:12.000Z","msg":"曾於西環明星海鮮燒鵝專門店出席聚會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"890c9f0f2cf79038cabd9f5028cd576500ac33ec","tid":1889340,"uid":308588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T15:15:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fCqdbNX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfCqdbNX.gif&h=5257c0e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd748fda2715ad64aa41cd0fd33dade6ac0a8159","tid":1889340,"uid":174013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T15:1